 Tykeran Hamilton , 25 , has been jailed for 11 years .
He killed cyclist Alan Knight in hit-and-run .
An unlicensed driver fresh off a vodka and cocaine binge shouted ` watch this ' before accelerating up to 70mph on a residential road at 7 am .
Hamilton sped down the road and overtook cars ` recklessly ' - narrowly avoiding a central reservation .
Hamilton admitted causing death by dangerous driving .